# Branch: stay on main

- The default and only working branch for this project is **main**.
- Do **not** create or switch to other branches unless the user explicitly asks.
- Do not suggest creating a new branch; always assume work goes on **main** (commit and push to main).
- When suggesting git commands (push, pull, checkout), use **main** so work stays on main.
- If the editor or UI offers "Create branch", ignore it and keep working on main.
